Matrix computation using openMÃ….
Computes and prints the sum of a equally sized matrix.
Also the position and size of the both the maximum value and the lowest value are printed.
The values are randomly selected between 0-98.

Standard and maximum value for MATRIX_SIZE is 100000. Minimum value is 1.
Standard and maximum value for NR_THREADS is 8.

write 'make' to build

Usage: matrixSum-openmp [MATRIX_SIZE] [NR_THREADS]


 

 